lines_and_colors: The Jay his Castanet has struck
Put on your muff for Winter
The Tippet that ignores his voice
Of Swarthy Days he is the close
The Cricket drops a sable line
No more from your's at present
document.title: The jay his castanet has struck
document.publication: The Poems of Emily Dickinson, Variorum Edition, Franklin, 1998
